<script>

    name: 'NavbarPage',
    components: {
      mdbNavbar,
      mdbNavbarBrand,
      mdbNavbarToggler,
      mdbNavbarNav,
      mdbNavItem,
      mdbDropdown,
      mdbDropdownMenu,
      mdbDropdownToggle,
      mdbDropdownItem,
      mdbInput
    }
  }
</script>

<template>

        </mdb-dropdown>
       
      </mdb-navbar-nav>
      <mdb-navbar-nav right>
        <mdb-nav-item to="/register">Register</mdb-nav-item>

      </mdb-navbar-nav>
    </mdb-navbar-toggler>
  </mdb-navbar>
</template>
